{% submission %}

{% submission-part type="problem" %}

I want my students to spend more time practicing German conversations, but there’s only one of me and 25+ of them. At lower levels they need practice with someone with good pronunciation and grammar that they can mimic. It’s frustrating that many resources have Spanish and French but not German.

{% /submission-part %}

{% submission-part type="proposed-solution" %}

I’d love for something that works on Chromebooks, because our district has a phone ban. I’d like to be able to record myself giving questions and prompts, and the student could give a range of verbal answers (think “I like to play BLANK”). The app would ideally accept the answer if the part of the response that isn’t open ended was correct and well pronounced enough.

{% /submission-part %}

{% /submission %}